        <!-- 1. Executive Summary -->
        <section id="executive-summary" class="section-card">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center gradient-text">1. Executive Summary: Redefining Personal Productivity</h2>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center mt-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="sub-title">Objective & Strategic Impact</h3>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed mb-4">This initiative aims to develop an innovative, AI-powered personal project management system. Its core objective is to directly address the escalating "productivity paradox," where existing tools often create more organizational overhead than actual efficiency gains for individuals.</p>
                    <p class="text-lg leading-relaxed">By leveraging a multi-agent AI architecture, our solution will automate mundane organizational tasks, thereby freeing up cognitive load and enabling unparalleled user focus and strategic execution.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-blue-50 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-md text-center">
                    <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-600 mb-2">Key Takeaway:</p>
                    <p class="text-3xl font-black text-blue-800 leading-tight">
                        A personalized, intelligent assistant that transforms raw thoughts into actionable, prioritized workflows.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 mt-4">🚀 Enhancing individual productivity & cognitive load management.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 2. The Opportunity -->
        <section id="the-opportunity" class="section-card">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center gradient-text">2. The Opportunity: Addressing the Productivity Paradox</h2>
            
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-10 mt-8">
                <div>
                    <h3 class="sub-title">Problem Statement: User Frustrations</h3>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg space-y-3 pl-4">
                        <li>**Current Tools are Overly Cumbersome:** Traditional PM platforms demand excessive time for *managing the tool* rather than *doing the work*.</li>
                        <li>**Information Overload & Fragmentation:** Brain dumps scatter across various apps (Google Keep, GitHub, etc.), leading to a fractured view of priorities.</li>
                        <li>**Executive Function Drain:** The continuous cognitive effort for organizing, prioritizing, and breaking down tasks hinders actual progress and leads to burnout.</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3 class="sub-title">Market Gap: The Demand for Intelligent Solutions</h3>
                    <div class="highlight-box mb-6">
                        <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">The Personal Productivity Software Market is projected to reach:</p>
                        <p class="text-5xl font-black text-purple-700">$45B by 2025</p>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-lg space-y-3 pl-4">
                        <li>High user dissatisfaction due to complexity (85% get lost in details, 78% cite poor integration).</li>
                        <li>Clear and growing demand for solutions that intelligently integrate, automate, and prioritize tasks.</li>
                    </ul>
                    <p class="text-lg mt-4 font-semibold text-blue-700">Our Unique Value Proposition: To create a system that *adapts to the user's thought process*, acting as an extension of their executive function, rather than another tool to be managed.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- 3. Project Vision -->
        <section id="project-vision" class="section-card">
            <h2 class="section-title text-center gradient-text">3. Project Vision: Your Personal AI Operations (AI-Ops) System</h2>
            <h3 class="sub-title text-center">Core Concept: Orchestrating AI Agents for Personal Productivity</h3>
            <p class="text-lg text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10">A centralized web application orchestrating a suite of specialized AI agents to manage the entire personal project lifecycle, from raw ideation to completion and retrospective, ensuring seamless workflow.</p>

            <div class="flex justify-center items-center mb-10">
                <div class="w-full lg:w-3/4 bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg shadow-inner">
                    <pre class="bg-gray-800 text-gray-50 text-sm p-4 rounded overflow-x-auto"><code>Your Brain Dump
      ↓
Web App (Frontend)
      ↓
API Gateway
      ↓
  AI Agents
      ↓
(Gemini API, GitHub API, Google Tasks/Keep API)
      ↓
Firestore Database
      ↓
Web App (Synchronized Views)
                    </code></pre>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h3 class="sub-title text-center mt-8">System Principles: Foundations of Intelligent Productivity</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mt-6">
