                <div class="agent-card p-4">
                    <span class="text-purple-600 agent-icon">🧠</span>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-purple-800">Intelligent Assistance</p>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Leverage AI for understanding, structuring, and prompting.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="agent-card p-4">
                    <span class="text-green-600 agent-icon">🔗</span>
                    <p class="font-semibold text-lg text-green-800">Seamless Integration</p>
